<subSubSection id="C33841B9BB4DFFC225AECCAEFADFE422" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" type="description">
<paragraph id="8B9D1232BB4DFFC225AECCAEFE72E549" blockId="6.[151,1436,925,1144]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">
<bibRefCitation id="EFB36FC3BB4DFFC225AECCAEFED2E286" author="Barroso, G. M." box="[151,336,925,951]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref6519" refString="Barroso, G. M. (1976) Subtribo Baccharidinae Hoffman. Estudo das especies ocorrentes no Brasil. Rodriguesia 28: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="1976">Barroso (1976)</bibRefCitation>
referred to the specimen 
<emphasis id="B956CE20BB4DFFC227B2CCAEFC9EE287" box="[651,796,925,950]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">Dusén 6906</emphasis>
as “ 
<typeStatus id="5499AC90BB4DFFC2266BCCAEFC40E286" box="[850,962,925,951]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">holotype</typeStatus>
” of 
<taxonomicName id="4C2269B1BB4DFFC226CECCAEFB2EE287" box="[1015,1196,925,950]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Baccharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="curitybensis">
<emphasis id="B956CE20BB4DFFC226CECCAEFB2EE287" box="[1015,1196,925,950]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">B. curitybensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, without indicating which duplicate she was referring to and in which herbarium it is located. Barroso’s choice was the first-step for lectotypification and the specimen 
<emphasis id="B956CE20BB4DFFC22755CCD9FD7FE532" box="[620,765,1002,1027]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">Dusén 6906</emphasis>
at S (S10-22254) is here designated as 
<typeStatus id="5499AC90BB4DFFC221D8CCD9FACDE535" box="[1249,1359,1002,1028]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">lectotype</typeStatus>
in the second-step to accomplish the ICBN requirements (McNeil 
<emphasis id="B956CE20BB4DFFC226B1CB22FC45E51B" box="[904,967,1041,1066]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">et al.</emphasis>
2006). This designation restricts and specifies 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB36FC3BB4DFFC2243FCB0BFE4CE563" author="Barroso, G. M." box="[262,462,1080,1106]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47" pagination="1 - 281" refId="ref6519" refString="Barroso, G. M. (1976) Subtribo Baccharidinae Hoffman. Estudo das especies ocorrentes no Brasil. Rodriguesia 28: 1 - 281." type="journal article" year="1976">Barroso’s (1976)</bibRefCitation>
choice and results in several isolectotypes for this name. The remaining 
<typeStatus id="5499AC90BB4DFFC2200DCB0BFA19E563" box="[1332,1435,1080,1106]" pageId="6" pageNumber="47">syntypes</typeStatus>
don’t have known duplicates.
</paragraph>
